{"build_type":"library","description":"Clean launch worker for the shared-epilogue proof: receives its context (per-instance region pointer) as the first argument, brackets its arena (prologue capture), computes a constant result (84), and hands it to the shared worker epilogue, which writes it into the region and exits. The author writes only the logic plus the epilogue handoff; the epilogue is the shared runtime reference (worker-runtime-FINAL A7), not inlined. Auto-weaving the prologue/epilogue via a build aspect is the next refinement.","module_name":"produce-launch-worker-constant-result","package_name":"produce-launch-worker-constant-result","function_definitions":{"produce-launch-worker-constant-result":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"context","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"answer","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":84},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"apply-worker-epilogue-writing-result-toward-context-region","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"context"},{"kind":"var","value":"answer"}],"result_assignment_variable":"_e","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"answer"}}]}}}